tatic\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531866\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 06, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rzu1665702997024.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rzu1665702997024.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rzu1665702997024.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rzu1665702997024\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                  \n                  Configuring a License File Manually\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rzu1665702997024__p_d67460e1_d67461e1_d67462e1\">To configure a license later, you can do one of the following:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rzu1665702997024__li_d30173e1_d30174e1_d30175e1\">Copy your license file to <span class=\"ph filepath\">C:/Program Files (x86)/Common Files/SafeNet Sentinel/Sentinel RMS License Manager/WinNT</span>, then restart the Sentinel RMS License Manager service. For more information about generating this file, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mwx1665702749228.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mwx1665702749228.html\" title=\"You are given an Entitlement ID when you register with Uniface, which allows you to access the Sentinel EMS customer portal, where you can lock your license to a specific machine and obtain the actual license file.\">Configuring Network On-Premises Served Licenses</a>.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rzu1665702997024__li_d30176e1_d30177e1_d30178e1\">Use the Sentinel RMS License Manager Administration tool (<span class=\"ph filepath\">WlmAdmin.exe</span>) to configure your license.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rzu1665702997024__li_d30179e1_d30180e1_d30181e1\">Activate your network cloud-served license using the\n                                Uniface License Management utility (<span class=\"ph filepath\">ulic</span>). For\n                                more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"izl1665702748868.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/izl1665702748868.html\" title=\"A network cloud-served license enables a Sentinel RMS License Manager to run concurrent licenses from a network location\">Configuring Network Cloud-Served Licenses</a>. </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rzu1665702997024__p_d67463e1_d67464e1_d67465e1\">The RMS tools are located in <span class=\"ph filepath\">C:/Program Files (x86)/Common Files/SafeNet Sentinel/Tools</span>.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"rzu1665702997024__note_w3519ab1b5b7_w3520ab1b5_w3521ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> \n                  If you start the RMS License Manager or Sentinel Cloud Plug-in before configuring your license, restart these services once your license is configured.</div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531866\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531866\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Configuring a License File Manually Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 06, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Configuring a License File Manually To configure a license later, you can do one of the following: Copy your license file to C:/Program Files (x86)/Common Files/SafeNet Sentinel/Sentinel RMS License Manager/WinNT , then restart the Sentinel RMS License Manager service. For more information about generating this file, see Configuring Network On-Premises Served Licenses . Use the Sentinel RMS License Manager Administration tool ( WlmAdmin.exe ) to configure your license. Activate your network cloud-served license using the Uniface License Management utility ( ulic ). For more information, see Configuring Network Cloud-Served Licenses . The RMS tools are located in C:/Program Files (x86)/Common Files/SafeNet Sentinel/Tools . Note: If you start the RMS License Manager or Sentinel Cloud Plug-in before configuring your license, restart these services once your license is configured. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}